			"system":{
				"description":{
					"value":"<p class=\"flavour\"><i>A featureless white mist roils within each of the stone archways set around the chamber</i></p><p><b>Trap:</b> Acererak has laid this trap for adventurers who have studied the lore of the Tomb of Horrors and who hope to unravel the workings of what they assume are teleportation circles.</p>",
